(4, 'fleet.php', 'Our Fleet', 'Check Our Fleet - two ton van Four ton and Eight ton truck | Singh Movers', '', 'Singh Movers provides fleet for hire according to moving needs for small of two ton van to large move with eight ton truck. Call 0423682368', '', '', 'Melbourne', '', '', '', 'hire-removalists-truck-with-man-and-van', '<div class=\"col-md-12\"><h2 class=\"bg-warning text-center p-3 text-black font-weight-bold mb-5\">OUR FLEET</h2></div><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"images/2 ton removal van australia.jpg\" alt=\"2 ton removal van\" title=\"2 ton removalists van\" width=\"300\" /></div>     \r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"justify\"><h4 style=\"font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase\">2 Ton van</h4>     A van of this size can usually cope with a small sized house move. Unless youre a serious hoarder, you will probably be able to fit your belongings from anything up to a one-bedroom house into a domestic removals van like this. </div>      \r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div><hr />        \r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"images/4 ton truck.png\" alt=\"4 ton renoval truck\" title=\"4 ton removalists truck\" width=\"300\" height=\"190\" /></div> \r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"justify\"><h4 style=\"font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase\">4 Ton truck</h4>     This size vehicle can usually cope with a small to average-sized house move. This is suitable up to a two-bedroom house into a domestic removals. <br /><br /></div>            \r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div><hr />        \r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"images/6 ton removalist truck.jpg\" alt=\"8 ton removal truck\" title=\"8 ton removalists truck\" height=\"190\" width=\"300\" /></div> \r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"justify\"><h4 style=\"font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase\">8 Ton truck</h4>     For a bigger house move, you might want to choose one of these larger, purpose-built vehicles. Children have a habit of pretty much doubling the amount of stuff we need, so these vehicles are ideal for families with children. <br /><br /></div>              \r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div><hr />        \r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"images/12 ton removalist truck melbourne.JPG\" alt=\"12 tone removal truck\" title=\"12 ton removalists truck\" height=\"215\" width=\"335\" /></div> \r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\" align=\"justify\"><h4 style=\"font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase\">12 Ton truck</h4>     For villas type move, you need to choose our larger truck for most heavy equipments. This type of truck suitable for families. <br /><br /></div>  ', '2020-10-24 04:17:55', '4', 1),
(5, 'price.php', 'Price', 'Price List | Singh Movers', '', 'Singh Movers provide quality services at lowest price for house, office and furniture removal services Australia wide .', '', '', 'Melbourne', '', '', '', 'van-with-man-price', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1 class=\"col-md-12\"><img alt=\"Singh movers and packers cost and price list | van with a man price tag\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"images/PRICE-TAG.jpg\" title=\"Singh movers and packers Price tag\" /></h1>\r\n<!--<div class=\"col-md-3\" align=\"center\"><br /><br /><div class=\"btn btn-info\" style=\"height:40px; line-height:28px; font-weight:bold; width:182px\">GET A FREE QUOTE</div></div>-->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\"><img alt=\"2 ton removal truck\" src=\"images/2 ton removal van australia.jpg\" style=\"width:300px\" title=\"2 ton furniture removalists van\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<h4>2 Ton van</h4>\r\nA van of this size can usually cope with a small sized house move. Unless youre a serious hoarder, you will probably be able to fit your belongings from anything up to a one-bedroom house into a domestic removals van like this.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>55$ Per Hour including GST (1 Man and 2 Ton Van)</li>\r\n	<li>75$ Per Hour including GST (2 Men and 2 Ton Van)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\"><img alt=\"4 tone removal truck\" src=\"images/4 ton truck.png\" style=\"width:300px\" title=\"4 ton furniture removalists van\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<h4>4 Ton truck</h4>\r\nThis size vehicle can usually cope with a small to average-sized house move. This is suitable up to a two-bedroom house into a domestic removals.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>70$ Per Hour + Gst (1 Man and 4 Ton Truck)</li>\r\n	<li>85$ Per Hour including GST (2 Men and 4 Ton Truck)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\"><img alt=\"8 ton removal truck\" src=\"images/6 ton removalist truck.jpg\" style=\"width:300px\" title=\"8 ton furniture removalists truck\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<h4>6 Ton truck</h4>\r\nFor a bigger house move, you might want to choose one of these larger, purpose-built vehicles. Children have a habit of pretty much doubling the amount of stuff we need, so these vehicles are ideal for families with children.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>95$ Per Hour including GST (2 Men and 6 Ton Truck)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\"><img alt=\"8 ton removal truck\" src=\"images/6 ton removalist truck.jpg\" style=\"width:300px\" title=\"8 ton furniture removalists truck\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<h4>8 - 10 Ton truck</h4>\r\nFor a bigger house move, you might want to choose one of these larger, purpose-built vehicles. Children have a habit of pretty much doubling the amount of stuff we need, so these vehicles are ideal for families with children.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>110$ Per Hour including GST (2 Men and 8 - 10 Ton Truck)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\"><img alt=\"12 ton removal truck\" src=\"images/12 ton removalist truck melbourne.JPG\" style=\"height:193px; width:329px\" title=\"ton furniture removalists truck\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<h4>12 Ton truck</h4>\r\nFor a Villas or multiple house at once, you might want to choose one of these our largest, purpose-built vehicles. So these vehicles are ideal for Joint families with children in Melbourne.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>125$ Per Hour including GST (2 Men and 12 Ton Truck)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2020-10-04 16:48:50', '5', 1),
(6, 'insurance.php', 'Insurance', 'Insurance of Furniture Moving Protection | Singh Movers', '', 'Singh Movers professionally provide insurance to your broken or cracked furniture by incident during a move.', '', '', 'Melbourne', '', '', '', 'furniture-moving-protection', '<div class=\"col-md-8 col-xs-12 col-sm-8 p-5 text-black\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-black\"><strong>Insurance</strong></h1>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>Singh Movers takes all the necessary care to ensure that your goods arrive safely at your next destination. To Protect the interest of our customers against accidents we have Transit and Public liability insurance. We do not charge extra every time for this insurance cover, only if a claim is made an access of $500 applies to customer.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Details as below :-</h5>\r\n\r\n<p>Upto $10,000 of any damage caused to your goods during transit as a result of truck accident, fire or overturning , a $500 access applies to customers in case of claim.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Public Liability insurance covers</li>\r\n	<li>Compensation can be Upto $10 million.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a history of zero damage, as we use professional removal techniques in our moves. We do our best to protect your belongings and as a company we carry the above mentioned Insurance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 pt-5\"><img alt=\"Insurance offer\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"images/insurance-image.jpg\" title=\"Secure equipment with singh movers protection\" /></div>\r\n', '2020-10-24 03:50:12', '6', 1),
