(9, '', 'Antique Furniture Removal', 'antique-removal', 'antique-furniture-removal', '<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</h4>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background: #ffd747; padding: 5px; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>\r\n<h1>Antique Furniture Removal</h1></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"background: #ffd747; padding: 5px; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>\r\n<h3>Need Your Precious Antique Furniture Or Art Relocated? Use Singh Movers And Packers Furniture Removalists Service</h3></strong></span></div>\r\n<!--<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Need your precious antique furniture or art relocated? Use Singh Movers and Packers Furniture removalists service</strong></span></span></span></p>-->\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\nWhat does an</span><strong>  antique furniture removal do?</strong>\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\n Yes, as the name suggests, they do move and remove <strong>antique furniture.</strong> But to consider this as their only function would be a huge fallacy. Most <strong>Furniture removalists </strong> you have ever seen working or have heard about are employees of moving and storage companies, as well as <strong>Singh Movers furniture Removalist.</strong>\r\n </span>\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\nThis gives testament to the fact that </span><strong> Furniture removalists</strong>\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\"> are responsible for dealing with not only furniture but appliances, moving boxes and various other things involved with moving and removals.\r\nYou might have seen a lot of freelance  Furniture removalists &nbsp;</span><strong>Furniture removalists</strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\"> &nbsp; on classified websites, offering their expert moving services to those in need. But these freelance movers only move your belongings from one floor to another, \r\nor from your house till the moving truck. That is the total extent of their responsibilities. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">But when your work with reliable </span><strong> Furniture removalists</strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">, who are associated with a moving company of some repute, you will see that their job responsibilities include</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Creating an inventory of items to be packed\r\n</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Packing all your belongings in the most secure and efficient way</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Loading all your packed belongings in one or many moving trucks</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Driving the truck to your new home or business location</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Unloading all items in the back of the trucks</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Carrying them inside the premises</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Unpacking them as efficiently as possible</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">The above list sums up the basic job responsibilities of a </span><strong> Furniture removalists</strong>\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">. But if you think for a second that the job of </span><strong>affordable Furniture  removalists in Australia </strong>\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">is easy, and anyone can do it, you would be sadly mistaken. Let us now take an in-depth look what a</span><strong> Furniture removalists</strong>\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">  usually does for you:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">The job of a <strong>Furniture removalists</strong> or <strong> Antique removals </strong> involves a lot of heavy lifting, being focused and on their feet at all times, and the added pressure of taking care of every item they pack, unpack, load or unload. Punctuality is also a big worry for all <strong>Antique Furniture removalists.</strong> You might ask WHY, but in all honesty, the answer is so simple that you did not even have to ask the question.</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Whenever you hire the services of <strong>furniture removalist services,</strong> you sign a service contract with them. This service contract includes some terms and conditions, one of them being the time frame within which your belongings will be delivered from your old home to the new one.</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">Now if a <strong>Furniture removalists services </strong> does not stick to a fixed schedule, he will end up compromising his punctuality, which would legally mean a breach of contract. So, to avoid such issues,<strong>Furniture removalists </strong> must always stress about being on time at all places.</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">If you were smart enough to pack your own boxes, then a <strong> furniture removalists</strong> will go through all the boxes and items of <strong>furniture </strong> you have packed and put numbered or coloured stickers on them. The numbers or colours of these stickers will be noted down on the inventory sheet you created, or they created for you, in accordance with the items packed. There are two copies of the inventory sheet, one for you, the customer, and one for the movers. You need to check each and every item in the sheet and match them with the numbers or colours yourself to make sure that everything is in order.<br>\r\nThe <a href=\"https://singhmovers.com.au/furniture-removalists\">furniture removalists </a> specialize in shifting heavyweight furniture to a brand new location without any hassle. In a few cases, if the staircase of any house remains too narrow for bringing down huge furniture to the moving truck, they use crane and additional accessories to make sure those can be shifted without any scratch on it. For moving the small furniture, they use packing pads and other fillers to make sure the furniture remain in place. However, not all the companies have the right equipment and accessories to move huge furniture like <strong> antique removals , piano removals , pool table removals or spa removalists.</strong> Therefore, it is mandatory to ask before you make the final deal.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">The</span><strong> furniture removalists</strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\"> specialize in shifting heavyweight furniture to a brand new location without any hassle. In a few cases, if the staircase of any house remains too narrow for bringing down huge furniture to the moving truck, they use crane and additional accessories to make sure those can be shifted without any scratch on it. For moving the small furniture, they use packing pads and other fillers to make sure the furniture remain in place. However, not all the companies have the right equipment and accessories to move huge furniture like</span><strong> antique removals , </strong><strong>piano removals </strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">, </span><strong>pool table removals </strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">or </span><strong>spa removalists</strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">. Therefore, it is mandatory to ask before you make the final deal.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\n	Another vital job responsibility that <strong>Furniture removalists </strong> perform is securing all your packed belongings in the back of the truck. \r\n	You might be of the opinion that a Furniture removalists simply stashes a packing box or a piece of furniture in the back of the truck and that is the end of it. \r\n	But actually, <a href=\"https://singhmovers.com.au/house-removalists\">House  removalists </a>  or <strong>antique removalists</strong> has to strap everything in with extreme caution, so that nothing moves around uncontrollably when the truck is in motion.\r\n</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\n	When the removals truck or trucks move, items stashed at the back have a tendency to collide with each other.\r\n	This sort of collision usually causes scrapes or scratches, which can often be damaging as well as depressing.\r\n	The job of a <strong>furniture removalists </strong> here is to wrap all the packed items that are susceptible to collision, scrapes and scratches.\r\n	A thick covering of blankets usually acts as a layer of protection and helps to keep everything intact, without damage, and scratch-free.\r\n\r\n	</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\n	When the moving trucks arrive at your new home, the <strong>antique removals </strong>unusually unload all the boxes from the trucks and carry them inside your home or apartment.\r\n	Some movers might also make it a point to place each box and each item of furniture in the right rooms so as to lend you a helping hand.\r\n	</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\nThe job of the <strong>Furniture removalists </strong> does not end with unloading the goods. \r\nAfter the unloading process has been completed, \r\nthe inventory list needs to be taken care off.\r\n Both the customer and the <strong>Furniture removalists</strong> will cross off each item or each packed box of the inventory list by coordinating the entries with the number of colour labels, \r\n so as to make sure that each and every box and piece of furniture has arrived at the customers new home, and has been unloaded.\r\n\r\n	</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\" ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\" ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\nNow that we have read about the job responsibilities of a </span>\r\n<strong>Furniture removalists, </strong>\r\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:times new roman\">\r\nNow that we have read about the job responsibilities of a Antique Furniture Removal